<Paragraph Margin="0,0" FontSize="12" Foreground="silver">Some things in Minecraft, like seeds, are very small. Other things just look small because theyâ€™re far away. Until recently it was literally impossible to tell the difference.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph Margin="0,0" Foreground="black">Minecraft ä¸­æœ‰ä¸€äº›ç‰©å“æœ¬èº«å°±ååˆ†ç»†å°ï¼Œæ¯”å¦‚ç§å­ï¼›è¿˜æœ‰ä¸€äº›ç‰©ä½“åªæ˜¯å› ä¸ºè·ç¦»è¾ƒè¿œæ‰çœ‹èµ·æ¥å°ã€‚åœ¨ä¸ä¹…å‰ï¼Œä½ æ˜¯æ— æ³•ç¡®åˆ‡çœ‹å‡ºè¿™ç±»ç‰©ä½“çš„å…·ä½“åˆ†åˆ«çš„ã€‚</Paragraph>
<Paragraph Margin="0,0" FontSize="12" Foreground="silver">Luckily, in the first part of the Caves and Cliffs update, we added an item that can help. Itâ€™s the spyglass, and itâ€™s our item of the week.</Paragraph>
